name: United 737-924/ER [N27477] Onboard Takeoff from Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
My very first time flying on a 737-900! An awesome takeoff on YYC's Runway 29, and a great way to start my San Diego vacation! :D I flew this 739 to Denver, and onwards to San Diego, both flights being operated by 737s. I'll making a trip report eventually, but only the YYC-DEN leg, because I wanted to save some memory on my camera. Anyway, I hope you guys enjoy this beautiful afternoon takeoff!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
